<title>chūn tiān yòu lái dào 迦南910</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 chūn tiān yòu lái dào, zhuǎn yǎn yòu yī nián. shí guāng rú liú shuǐ, dàn zhǐ huī shǒu jiān.
 fēng zhōng chuán jié bào, jiā jiā yǒu xiào yán. yé sū ài wǒ dà zhōng huá, xǔ duō shēng mìng bèi gǎi biàn.
 wǒ men jīn tiān yī tóng lái dào fù miàn qián, xiàn shàng gǎn ēn de xīn, bǎ wǒ men jiǎn xuǎn.
 hái yǒu hěn duō de zhòng rèn, wǒ men yī qǐ lái dān. zhè shì wǒ men hěn jiǔ de xīn yuàn, hěn jiǔ de xīn yuàn.</lyrics>
</song>